\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有條女截停我叫我聽下佢機構做d乜<br />\n見得閒聽佢講下<br />\n仲要懶熱情搭身搭世<br />\n原來係要join月費捐款"},{"pid":"938367837c442efbf2a942dbdf0cc8c7f9f32b3a","tid":53731,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:11:39.000Z","msg":"見過求職網有<br />\n$12000-$18000一個月（視乎做成幾多生意）"},{"pid":"7c6a60e12ffa6309dedf1c0e9c429c5800ea112e","tid":53731,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"行政費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548fb8bf2b8ba99a08b455267ea996c755f621bf","tid":53731,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"見佢地係咁呃人 好睇唔過眼"},{"pid":"fa262b23499df79466539bf36d538ccbf492ad53","tid":53731,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:25:01.000Z","msg":"緊係，唔係邊個同你企街"}]}